item.description: We have hunted at Hamilton Woods (some know it as Chebacco Woods) in Hamilton several times in the past couple of years and have always found many different varieties of fungi. The paths are easy to walk, and there are maps at the trail head. The address is 275 Chebacco Rd. in South Hamilton Ma. I still have a few baskets left for those who want one. Thsy are 50 cents each. Hope to see you there!
item.how_to_find_us: Parking is along the side of the road at the woods entrance
item.name: Mushroom Hunt at Hamilton Woods in Hamilton,Ma.
